86
00:04:13,985 --> 00:04:20,473
yo. mayne eltern hobn geshribn mikh ⟨in⟩ a ukraynishe. kh'hob nisht gehat azoy lib di ukraynishe

87
00:04:20,473 --> 00:04:22,175
shprakhe, ober

88
