209
00:11:01,748 --> 00:11:04,440
yo. un,

210
00:11:04,228 --> 00:11:05,200
⟨RUS-...⟩

211
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:08,284
vos gedenkt ir fun di tsayt ven di

212
