236
00:12:20,390 --> 00:12:24,542
ikh hob ayngepakt ales, ober shikh, geblibn nor oyf di fis,

237
00:12:24,542 --> 00:12:30,504
un ⟨ikh bin⟩ gegangen dray vokhn BAREGEL, iz gevorn tserisn. ikh bin gekumen BEGERMANYA,

238
00:12:31,033 --> 00:12:33,392
shoyn ⟨m-⟩ iz geven SHELEG.

239
00:12:33,392 --> 00:12:37,763
⟨ikh bin⟩ geven mit a shmate, hob tserisn epes a zakh, ikh gedenk nisht vos,

240
00:12:37,763 --> 00:12:39,819
un, geviklt di fis.

241
00:12:38,728 --> 00:12:42,164
y- yo, ober vu hot men aykh genemen, di GERMANIM,

242
00:12:42,340 --> 00:12:43,836
