256
00:13:27,210 --> 00:13:37,949
UNK dos iz geven MISHPAKHOT fun dem, vu kh'hob gevoynt iz geven MISHPAKHOT, zenen gekumen voynen. dort iz geven a geto shtub, iz, dortn zenen gekumen voynen MISHPAKHA f⟨un⟩,

257
00:13:37,949 --> 00:13:39,455
vu kh'hob gevoynt,

258
00:13:39,495 --> 00:13:41,278
fun di froy,

259
00:13:41,622 --> 00:13:46,172
iz geven MISHPAKHOT ire un zey zenen gekumen voynen tsuzamen mit zey.

260
00:13:46,650 --> 00:13:49,440
un, m'hot gekent geyn arbetn

261
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:50,998
funem geto?

262
00:13:49,603 --> 00:13:55,824
yo, a por sho, a por sho, nisht a gantse tog. m'hot, m'hot gekent nor a por sho geyn.

263
00:13:55,678 --> 00:13:57,596
un s'iz gevezn arbet?

264
00:13:58,294 --> 00:14:06,050
yo, z⟨i⟩, mayne shnayderin hot gehat arbet. zi hot gearbet far, artistkes, far, far groyse,

265
00:14:06,090 --> 00:14:08,801
vikhtike BAKHUROT zi hot gearbet.

266
00:14:09,195 --> 00:14:11,467
 un m'hot ir gegebn nokh arbet?

267
00:14:11,305 --> 00:14:13,543
yo, zi hot nokh gehat a bisele.

268
00:14:13,465 --> 00:14:16,749
 un s'iz gevezn vos tsu esn?

269
00:14:13,819 --> 00:14:15,483
zi hot nokh gehat a bis⟨l⟩.

270
00:14:16,806 --> 00:14:18,656
yo, esn iz geven.

271
00:14:18,291 --> 00:14:19,955
yo? tsu koyfn?

272
00:14:18,865 --> 00:14:22,116
⟨yo⟩, oyf KARTISIM, m'hot gegebn broyt.

273
00:14:23,050 --> 00:14:27,026
broyt iz geven oyf KARTISIM un⟨, ikh veys n-,⟩ s'iz geven.

274
00:14:27,792 --> 00:14:30,503
un, vi lang, hot ir...?

275
00:14:29,496 --> 00:14:33,298
do ven iz geven MILKHAMA, akht un fertsiker yor, ⟨iz⟩ oykh geven.

276
00:14:33,298 --> 00:14:37,404
in andere pletser iz nisht geven aza sheyne vayse broyt do bay undz.

277
00:14:37,478 --> 00:14:40,310
TODA LAEL az s'iz geven BEEMET.

278
00:14:40,718 --> 00:14:41,890
vos?

279
00:14:41,427 --> 00:14:44,222
un vi lang hot ir gevoynt in geto?

280
00:14:44,667 --> 00:14:47,650
dos ikh gedenkt nisht BEEMET.

281
00:14:48,902 --> 00:14:55,613
kh'hob nisht keyn anung vifl dos hot gekent zayn. ikh meyn a halb yor oder SHLOSHET REVII SHANA.

282
00:14:55,450 --> 00:14:57,736
un dernokh, vos hot pasirt?

283
00:14:57,880 --> 00:15:00,608
⟨nu,⟩ zog ikh, gekumen di GERMANIM,

284
00:15:01,052 --> 00:15:08,610
un zey..., nisht di GERMANIM, di HUNGARIM vos zey hobn gearbet mit di GERMANIM, zey hobn geklungen un zey hobn, gezogt, ale YEHUDIM

285
00:15:08,610 --> 00:15:11,120
zoln aropkumen fun di shtok,

286
00:15:11,363 --> 00:15:12,842
un di...

287
00:15:14,535 --> 00:15:22,426
un zey hobn oysgeveylt, zey hobn gemakht SELEKTSYA, vosere GIL. ikh gedenk nisht, fun akhtsn yor biz,

288
00:15:22,787 --> 00:15:28,854
biz finef un draysik, biz fertsik, hot men genemen, un di andere zenen aroyf tsurik in di shtub.

289
00:15:28,854 --> 00:15:30,757
ikh hob nisht gezen, ⟨nor⟩ undz ze'mir shoyn

290
00:15:30,757 --> 00:15:33,989
ongehoybn tsu geyn in a fabrik fun,

291
00:15:33,989 --> 00:15:36,399
tsigl-fabrik. vi azoy zogt men "tsigl"?

292
00:15:36,996 --> 00:15:38,846
es iz gut in yidish.

293
00:15:38,785 --> 00:15:40,342
tsigl-fabrik.

294
00:15:40,506 --> 00:15:42,083
BET KHAROSHET...

295
00:15:42,531 --> 00:15:46,204
 ikh veys, vi zol ikh zogn, ⟨aza⟩ tsigl-fabrik, nu...

296
00:15:46,564 --> 00:15:49,713
efsher mayn man iz do, volt er gevust tsu zogn.

297
00:15:47,593 --> 00:15:49,607
⟨L- L-⟩ UNK.

298
00:15:49,607 --> 00:15:52,937
un, vi lang zent ir gevezn dort?

299
00:15:53,044 --> 00:15:54,067
vu?

300
00:15:53,095 --> 00:15:54,456
in der fabrik.

301
00:15:54,462 --> 00:16:00,784
a! m'hot ongehoybn teykef tsu geyn. m'hot undz gefirt in di fabrik un teykef hot ongehoybn di transport.

302
00:16:00,638 --> 00:16:01,526
vu?

303
00:16:02,055 --> 00:16:06,065
m'hot ongehoybn tsu geyn biz, di, biz tsu di GVUL,

304
00:16:06,055 --> 00:16:06,977
⟨⟩.

305
00:16:06,072 --> 00:16:08,428
yedn tog draysik kilometer.

306
00:16:08,637 --> 00:16:10,976
un vi lang hot ir gegangen?

307
00:16:10,223 --> 00:16:11,601
dray vokhn.

308
00:16:11,151 --> 00:16:15,601
dray... un, kent ir undz dertseyln vos iz gevezn ⟨d-⟩?

309
00:16:11,826 --> 00:16:12,782
KEN.

310
00:16:13,986 --> 00:16:18,154
a sakh mentshn zenen geshtorbn BEEMTSA HADEREKH: mener,

311
00:16:18,154 --> 00:16:20,696
oykh a sakh geshtorbn, un froyen.

312
00:16:20,702 --> 00:16:26,141
s'iz geven a shvere derekh. un esn, m'iz gekumen bay nakht, hot men gegebn epes a bisl MARAK.

313
00:16:26,141 --> 00:16:29,572
m'hot shoyn nisht gehat koyekh tsu shteyn in TOR nokh di MARAK.

314
00:16:29,815 --> 00:16:36,012
ikh hob gehat mitgenemen a por pushkelekh, epes konzervn hob ikh gehat. mit dos hob ikh gelebt.

315
00:16:36,012 --> 00:16:40,760
YERAKOT oyf di felder hot men gerisn, hot men gegesn, ober azoy...

316
00:16:42,268 --> 00:16:46,261
a gantse tog gegangen. s'iz geven regn

317
00:16:46,352 --> 00:16:49,096
KOL HAYOM. s'iz shoyn geven nokh,

318
00:16:49,997 --> 00:16:54,412
, nokh ROSH HASHANA ⟨ven⟩ heybt on di regn shoyn.

319
00:16:51,889 --> 00:16:54,142
⟨s-⟩.

320
00:16:54,486 --> 00:16:59,188
KOL HAYOM HAYA GESHEM VEKAKH HALAKHNU BAGESHEM.

321
00:16:59,380 --> 00:17:00,909
BAGESHEM HALAKHNU.

322
00:17:03,328 --> 00:17:06,140
⟨VE-⟩ vu hot ir, zent geshlofn?

323
00:17:07,159 --> 00:17:08,840
vu undz ze'mir geshlofn?

324
00:17:09,031 --> 00:17:13,239
vu m'iz gekumen: in a REFET fun khazeyrim, fun KHAZIRIM,

325
00:17:13,239 --> 00:17:18,605
a REFET fun ferd, a REFET fun, fun UNK nisht keyn betn ho'mir gehat,

326
00:17:18,605 --> 00:17:20,030
bikhlal nisht.

327
00:17:20,030 --> 00:17:21,986
azoy oyf di fraye feld.

328
00:17:22,161 --> 00:17:26,880
di ershte nakht, a, a ROFA iz gevorn MESHUGA. zi hot gezen

329
00:17:27,071 --> 00:17:32,955
vos iz di MATSAV, ⟨me⟩, ver se firt undz, vu me firt undz, un oyf d- dr'erd shloft men;

330
00:17:33,096 --> 00:17:38,996
⟨zi iz⟩ gevorn m- meshuge. dos ikh gedenk azoy vi haynt. m'hot, geredt, ale mentshn dortn.

331
00:17:38,936 --> 00:17:41,460
ver iz zi gevezn, di froy?

332
00:17:41,483 --> 00:17:48,227
a ROFA, ROFA. ikh hob zi nisht gekent, nor vos andere hobn mir dertseylt az a ROFA iz gevorn MESHUGA,

333
00:17:41,938 --> 00:17:43,687
a doktor?

334
00:17:48,317 --> 00:17:52,124
vayl zi hot gezen di MATSAV, vu me firt undz un...

335
00:17:52,215 --> 00:17:54,251
ir gedenkt ire nomen?

336
00:17:53,768 --> 00:17:57,052
LO, ikh hob zi nisht gekent bikhlal, dos ikh zog,

337
00:17:57,092 --> 00:17:59,583
nor, vos ikh hob gehert fun andere,

338
00:17:59,860 --> 00:18:02,857
az a ROFA iz gevorn m- meshuge.

339
00:18:01,210 --> 00:18:06,058
 un ir hot derkent der mentshn, vos ir hot tsuzamen gegangen

340
00:18:06,058 --> 00:18:07,070
mit zey?

341
00:18:07,070 --> 00:18:09,134
ir hot derkent emetsn?

342
00:18:08,618 --> 00:18:13,265
LO, fuftsik yor tsurik, MA, vi ken men derkenen?

343
00:18:12,634 --> 00:18:18,343
NO, DAMALS, ir hot, gehat a FREUND, a, emetsn, tsi...?

344
00:18:16,836 --> 00:18:20,019
LO, kh'hob nisht gehat keynem. LO, LO.

345
00:18:18,343 --> 00:18:20,718
keynem nisht? aleyn?

346
00:18:20,394 --> 00:18:22,112
 in gantsn aleyn.

347
00:18:23,670 --> 00:18:27,005
oykh aleyn bin ikh avek fun, ⟨az m'iz⟩ gekumen tsurik

348
00:18:27,737 --> 00:18:31,106
nokh di lager, bin ikh avekgeforn oykh oyf YISRAEL,

349
00:18:31,450 --> 00:18:32,493
oykh aleyn.

350
00:18:32,493 --> 00:18:38,379
UNK ⟨nokh a mol⟩ in Budapest. fun Budapest, m'hot geshribn in di transport.

351
00:18:39,010 --> 00:18:42,331
s'iz geven a gantse transport, ze'mir geforn in OSTRIYA,

352
00:18:42,331 --> 00:18:44,556
di transport, un fun OSTRIYA

353
00:18:44,798 --> 00:18:48,418
oyf ITALYA, un dort ikh hob shoyn geheyratet.

354
00:18:46,921 --> 00:18:48,359
yo, UNK.

355
00:18:48,359 --> 00:18:52,216
un vos kent, vos gedenkt ir nokh fun der veg

356
00:18:52,527 --> 00:18:56,908
tsum, grenets? vos gedenkt ir funem dray vokhn?

357
00:18:58,180 --> 00:18:59,535
m'iz gegangen

358
00:18:59,535 --> 00:19:01,492
KOL YOM, dos gedenk ikh.

359
00:19:01,492 --> 00:19:03,169
vos ken ikh gedenken?

360
00:19:02,365 --> 00:19:04,721
un ver hot ⟨n-⟩ nisht gekent geyn?

361
00:19:05,065 --> 00:19:09,952
iz geshtorbn oyf di MAKOM. m'hot nisht getort tsugeyn helfn AFILU,

362
00:19:10,583 --> 00:19:15,352
rateven keynem. m'hot nisht getort tsugeyn. m'hot gedarft lozn shtarbn.

363
00:19:13,654 --> 00:19:17,461
un ven, ver hot, ge- ge- gegibt akhtung?

364
00:19:17,451 --> 00:19:18,559
oyf vemen?

365
00:19:18,092 --> 00:19:20,516
oyf aykh un oyf ale mentshn?

366
00:19:20,910 --> 00:19:29,578
a! dos iz di, oykh di ungarishe. biz tsu di GVUL iz geven oykh di ungarishe, NYILAS, vi azoy ikh zog; zey hobn gearbet mit di GERMANIM.

367
00:19:29,787 --> 00:19:34,535
zey hobn undz gefirt biz tsu di GVUL GERMANI.

368
00:19:34,731 --> 00:19:38,241
di GERMANIM hobn undz, genemen.

369
00:19:38,241 --> 00:19:40,119
zey hobn gefirt nokh,

370
00:19:40,119 --> 00:19:42,296
tsen kilometer BAREGEL,

371
00:19:42,296 --> 00:19:47,128
⟨un⟩ nokh dem hot men undz geleygt in vagonen, azoy vi ale YEHUDIM, m'hot gefirt in vagonen.

372
00:19:47,202 --> 00:19:49,558
host gezen vi azoy ale YEHUDIM m'hot gefirt?

373
00:19:48,602 --> 00:19:49,625
yo.

374
00:19:49,564 --> 00:19:52,170
azoy hot men undz gefirt oyf Landsberg.

375
00:19:52,618 --> 00:19:55,784
un vi lang zent ir gevezn in di vagonen?

376
00:19:56,331 --> 00:20:01,382
a! in di vagonen? geshlofn ho'mir nisht dort bay nakht, ho'mir gefort a gantse tog.

377
00:20:01,300 --> 00:20:02,376
eyn tog?

378
00:20:02,052 --> 00:20:04,888
yo. bay nakht, ⟨ikh⟩ gedenk ⟨nisht⟩.

379
00:20:02,710 --> 00:20:05,859
 vifl mentshn in a vagon?

380
00:20:05,089 --> 00:20:08,029
o, a sakh, zeyer a sakh!

381
00:20:09,139 --> 00:20:13,621
ze'mir ongekumen in Landsberg. dort iz geven oykh mener, in Landsberg.

382
00:20:14,522 --> 00:20:23,257
iz, di mener nebekh gelofn khapn a shtikele... vayl zey hobn, zey hobn gevust, s'iz do shtikelekh broyt fun di mentshn vos m'hot gegesn in di vagonen...

383
00:20:23,348 --> 00:20:26,429
zenen gelofn khapn shtikelekh broyt.

384
00:20:26,672 --> 00:20:29,619
UNK shtikelekh, nisht keyn gantse broyt.

385
00:20:30,182 --> 00:20:32,817
un di GERMANIM hobn un-

386
00:20:32,832 --> 00:20:39,857
mit di pasikn, mit gumi-pasikn geshlogn, un zey zenen nebekh aruntergelofn unter di RAKOVO- RAKEVET,

387
00:20:39,857 --> 00:20:42,377
vos ze'mir gekumen, di RAKEVET iz geshtanen,

388
00:20:42,450 --> 00:20:44,480
iz unter di RAKEVET

389
00:20:44,480 --> 00:20:47,962
zenen zey gelofn, di mentshn vos m'hot zey geshlogn,

390
00:20:48,002 --> 00:20:51,794
di GERMANIM, vayl zey hobn gegangen zukhn shtikelekh broyt.

391
00:20:52,879 --> 00:20:57,007
ikh hob oykh nisht gevust, vos, vos iz dos? mit PASIM,

392
00:20:57,115 --> 00:20:59,522
mener mit PASIM kleyder,

393
00:20:59,528 --> 00:21:03,524
un kh'hob gezen az di GERMANIM shlogn, hob ikh shoyn gezen, m'iz

394
00:21:03,524 --> 00:21:05,343
arayngefaln biter.

395
00:21:06,557 --> 00:21:08,064
un dernokh de⟨m⟩...

396
00:21:06,666 --> 00:21:08,499
⟨un⟩ vos hot ir gedakht?

397
00:21:08,792 --> 00:21:12,423
vos ikh hob ged- gedenkt, gekler- geklert?

398
00:21:10,463 --> 00:21:13,410
gedakht, gedakht, yo, geklert.

399
00:21:12,690 --> 00:21:16,869
az do iz di sof far YEHUDIM, dos hob ikh geklert.

400
00:21:17,280 --> 00:21:21,914
nu, a sakh mentshn iz geven ⟨BE-⟩ BEEMET geshtorbn, un m'hot gefirt in Dakhoy.

401
00:21:22,849 --> 00:21:26,505
mikh hot men gefirt in, TÜRKHEIM lager, ⟨ober⟩ s'iz geven...

402
00:21:25,650 --> 00:21:28,681
un vi lang zent ir gevezn in Landsberg?

403
00:21:29,143 --> 00:21:35,414
in Landsberg? nisht ⟨a zakh⟩, a por vokhn, ober nisht gearbet gornisht, ⟨vayl,⟩ s'iz geven aza MAAVAR,

404
00:21:35,809 --> 00:21:37,603
 lager MAAVAR.

405
00:21:37,603 --> 00:21:39,364
geven a por vokhn,

406
00:21:39,623 --> 00:21:48,071
mit holtserne shikh, ⟨hob ikh⟩ gekrign. ⟨ikh bin⟩ geven on, on shikh, nor mit a shmate arumgeviklt. ikh bin gekumen in GERMANYA, iz shoyn geven SHELEG.

407
00:21:48,415 --> 00:21:55,429
fun, dray vokhn gegangen. AKHAREY KHAGIM iz shoyn gevorn dortn KHOREF.

408
00:21:55,772 --> 00:21:58,334
 iz geven,

409
00:21:58,334 --> 00:22:03,596
transportn. mikh hot men ge- s'iz, geven BAKHUROT vos m'hot zey gefirt in,

410
00:22:03,720 --> 00:22:07,646
andere lagern, un mikh hot men gefirt, mikh un nokh froyen...

411
00:22:08,108 --> 00:22:12,658
ober, m'hot undz nisht gefirt shoyn in vagonen; m'hot undz gefirt in,

412
00:22:12,715 --> 00:22:15,780
RAKEVET PRATI, vi mentshn forn,

413
00:22:16,410 --> 00:22:22,081
azoy vi do f- do iz do RAKEVET, vos me kukt aroys fun di fentster. vi azoy ken heysn di...?

414
00:22:20,393 --> 00:22:23,745
yo. vifl mentshn zent ir gevezn?

415
00:22:23,194 --> 00:22:26,081
a! dos ken ikh oykh nisht gedenken.

416
00:22:24,797 --> 00:22:26,259
a sakh mentshn?

417
00:22:26,081 --> 00:22:29,145
nu, yo, nisht mikh aleyn hot men gefirt, BETAKH.

418
00:22:26,755 --> 00:22:28,876
.

419
00:22:29,168 --> 00:22:32,975
ober RAKEVET NORMALI, nisht keyn,

420
00:22:33,420 --> 00:22:39,199
azoy vi m'hot gefirt ale YEHUDIM, azoy farmakht vi di BEHEMOT.

421
00:22:39,199 --> 00:22:44,752
dos iz geven vegn mentshn RAKEVET. m'hot undz gefirt biz, fun Landsberg

422
00:22:45,047 --> 00:22:47,235
oyf, TROFAIACH,

423
00:22:47,325 --> 00:22:51,693
TR-... neyn, nisht TROFAIACH: TÜRKHEIM, TÜRKHEIM. ikh bin ale mol, TAUT hob ikh.

424
00:22:48,490 --> 00:22:49,858
TÜRKHEIM.

425
00:22:51,747 --> 00:22:54,103
TROFAIACH iz OSTRIYA geven.

426
00:22:53,113 --> 00:22:57,292
un vos iz gevezn az ir zent gekumen nokh TÜRKHEIM?

427
00:22:57,771 --> 00:23:04,052
nu, in TÜRKHEIM, m'hot gedarft vartn a halbe tog biz ven di ⟨m-⟩... dort iz geven oykh mener UNK

428
00:23:04,052 --> 00:23:05,817
mener-lager un froyen...

429
00:23:05,817 --> 00:23:10,289
m'hot gedarft vartn a halbe tog biz ven di mener hobn gemakht, BLOKIM,

430
00:23:10,289 --> 00:23:14,927
fun holts geboyt azoy shtiber, BLOKIM, shtiber, yene shtiber...

431
00:23:15,017 --> 00:23:18,552
BLOKIM azoy geboyt. m'hot gedarft vartn a halbe tog

432
00:23:19,270 --> 00:23:23,081
un s'iz geven fartik. ze'mir zekhtsik froyen in eyn blok,

433
00:23:23,081 --> 00:23:25,119
ze'mir geven, gevoynt.

434
00:23:25,918 --> 00:23:28,780
un ir hot getrofn emetsn bakant?

435
00:23:26,070 --> 00:23:26,823
UNK

436
00:23:28,281 --> 00:23:30,316
LO. LO.

437
00:23:28,804 --> 00:23:30,193
keyner nisht?

438
00:23:30,610 --> 00:23:34,007
bay undz iz geven di hoypt-kekher

439
00:23:34,007 --> 00:23:40,242
a goy, nor er iz geven, vegn POLITIKA m'hot im genemen. er iz geven gerekhnt azoy vi a yid.

440
00:23:40,242 --> 00:23:46,756
di, Royte Kreyts, di TSLAV ADOM, ven er hot geshikt di pekl, tsuker mit a SMIKHA,

441
00:23:46,756 --> 00:23:48,929
er oykh gekrign azoy a pekl.

442
00:23:49,341 --> 00:23:52,474
un iz gekumen fun Budapest a,

443
00:23:52,682 --> 00:24:03,425
iz gekumen demls a naye transport bay undz in, in lager, un er hot bakant a BAKHURA, a sheyne, a hoykhe YEHUDIYA. ERZSI hot zi geheysn. dos gedenk ikh, afile ir nomen.

444
00:24:03,533 --> 00:24:07,222
zi iz gegan- gegangen sheyn ongetun, mit a tikhele,

445
00:24:07,296 --> 00:24:09,585
mit a fartekh a sheyne.

446
00:24:09,625 --> 00:24:12,457
⟨a⟩ gantse tog hot zi geputst di negelekh.

447
00:24:12,105 --> 00:24:13,773
dortn?

448
00:24:12,457 --> 00:24:14,025
yo, yo.

449
00:24:13,773 --> 00:24:14,631
yo?

450
00:24:14,025 --> 00:24:18,970
nu, er iz geven MENAHEL, der gelibter.

451
00:24:18,970 --> 00:24:25,835
er hot zikh farlibt fun di ERZSI, un zi, er hot zi gemakht oykh a MENAHELET. ⟨zi hot⟩ gornisht gearbet, nor a gantse tog ⟨hot zi⟩

452
00:24:26,027 --> 00:24:30,678
gemakht di nogl, gegangen sheyn ongetun, mit a tikhele, mit a fa-...

453
00:24:31,191 --> 00:24:34,304
 EKH OMRIM? a shirtsl, fartekh.

454
00:24:34,937 --> 00:24:42,727
UNK er hot khasene gehat. ven s'⟨iz⟩ geendikt di MILKHAMA, ven s'iz gevorn SHIKHRUR, er hot khasene gehat mit ir.

455
00:24:44,083 --> 00:24:49,308
er iz geven a HOMOSEKSUAL. er hot gehat koydem a yingl, a BAKHUR fun POLANYA.

456
00:24:49,618 --> 00:24:52,143
er hot gehat a TSRIF lebn di kikh,

457
00:24:52,251 --> 00:24:59,728
un er hot geh- er iz geven HOMOSEKSUAL, un dernokh dem, PITOM, er ⟨hot⟩ khasene gehat mit di ERZSI.

458
00:24:59,728 --> 00:25:04,375
⟨mir ale⟩, kh'gedenk, "vos iz dos?" nu, er hot gevolt heyratn mit ir.

459
00:25:04,840 --> 00:25:10,334
er iz geven a goy; vegn POLITIKA m'hot im genemen. er iz nisht geven keyn YEHUD, a yid.

460
00:25:11,455 --> 00:25:15,668
un, nor dos. ikh hob gearbet in kikh zeyer shver.

461
00:25:15,792 --> 00:25:17,045
⟨in kikh⟩ UNK...

462
00:25:15,927 --> 00:25:17,693
vos hot men gearbet?

463
00:25:18,559 --> 00:25:24,757
m'hot gedarft helfn far di GERMANIM, ⟨, g-⟩ far di GERMANIM, hobn gehat a ungarishe kukher.

464
00:25:24,757 --> 00:25:28,813
di ungarishe kenen zeyer gut kokhn, zogt men.

465
00:25:29,494 --> 00:25:34,517
zey hobn gevolt a HUNGARI, iz er hot gekokht. ho'mir gedarft sheyln kartofl

466
00:25:34,722 --> 00:25:38,610
mit, ikh vey- kh'gedenk shoyn nisht vos BEEMET m'hot gedarft dortn...

467
00:25:38,610 --> 00:25:42,245
un far groyse ⟨KAZANA⟩ vos m'hot gekokht far di yidn,

468
00:25:42,403 --> 00:25:45,282
hot men gedarft vashn groyse ⟨KAZANIM⟩.

469
00:25:45,964 --> 00:25:47,476
s'iz geven a⟨rb-⟩...

470
00:25:46,099 --> 00:25:52,045
un ir hot gekent esn? ir hot gekent, gehat mer esn in kikh? UNK

471
00:25:48,681 --> 00:25:52,387
vos, voser...? LO. vosere esn?

472
00:25:52,900 --> 00:25:55,722
nisht geven mer esn bikhlal.

473
00:25:57,135 --> 00:26:01,227
un vos gedenkt ir, funem arbet?

474
00:25:57,253 --> 00:25:58,086
UNK

475
00:26:01,557 --> 00:26:06,090
⟨dernokh dem⟩, m'hot gearbet, als SABALIT, SABAL.

476
00:26:05,303 --> 00:26:06,934
a, dernokh dem?

477
00:26:06,805 --> 00:26:18,662
yo, eyn mol dos un eyn mol, SABAL, getrogn milekh far di... gegangen in dorf, dray kilometer, in TÜRKHEIM. iz geven a kleyne TNUVA dortn.

478
00:26:18,668 --> 00:26:22,779
⟨mir hobn⟩ gebrengt mit di AGALA. m'hot nisht ge- undz ze'mir geven di SUSIM.

479
00:26:23,275 --> 00:26:29,898
etlekhe froyen ze'mir gef- geshtupt, eyne hot geshtupt fornt, eyne hintn, ho'mir gebrengt KHALAV.

480
00:26:30,362 --> 00:26:33,764
un emetsn iz mit aykh gegangen, a...?

481
00:26:32,235 --> 00:26:43,501
yo, S.S. nor dos vil ikh zogn: di S.S. iz a bisl aroysgegangen, un der iz gev- dort iz geven a alte mentsh, hot gearbet bay di TNUVA. ikh hob gevoynt, nokh di SHIKHRUR hob ikh gevoynt bay im.

482
00:26:43,963 --> 00:26:50,254
zey hobn gegebn, dires tsu voynen. zey hobn gemeynt, az di AMERIKAIM zenen arayngekumen, m'vet makhn

483
00:26:50,254 --> 00:26:51,855
TSAROT far zey,

484
00:26:52,030 --> 00:26:57,103
hobn zey gezukht YEHUDIM, zey zoln voynen bay zey, az KEILU az zey hobn geholfn far undz.

485
00:26:57,632 --> 00:27:00,714
iz ven di GERMANI iz aroysgegangen,

486
00:27:00,923 --> 00:27:07,025
fleg er undz ale mol gebn far ale BAKHUROT dortn a bisele milekh tsu trinken. dos iz geven gut BEEMET.

487
00:27:07,538 --> 00:27:08,376
KEN.

488
00:27:07,605 --> 00:27:09,556
ir gedenkt zayn nomen?

489
00:27:09,310 --> 00:27:16,695
LO, dos nisht. ikh hob gevoynt bay zey, ober... er hot gehat a froy, oykhet a alte froy, er a alter mentsh.

490
00:27:17,157 --> 00:27:22,264
di nomen nisht, ober s'iz geven zeyer sheyn az er hot geholfn a bisl...

491
00:27:22,540 --> 00:27:29,527
un ⟨BE- do-⟩ un BEEMTSA HADEREKH iz geven gute daytshn oykhet. zey hobn a vorf gegebn a kleyne broyt,

492
00:27:29,527 --> 00:27:33,145
ho'mir in der heym gemakht KHALUKA fun dos,

493
00:27:33,145 --> 00:27:35,139
gegebn yedn a shtikele.

494
00:27:35,702 --> 00:27:40,471
KEN, s'iz geven gute GERMANIM oykhet. zey hobn gehat RAKHMANUT oyf undz. ⟨ober GE-⟩

495
00:27:40,478 --> 00:27:45,782
veyst ver iz geven di GERMANIM? ukraynIM zenen geven ongetun alts, S.S.n,

496
00:27:45,782 --> 00:27:48,892
S.S. kleyder, ukraynishe BAKHURIM,

497
00:27:49,185 --> 00:27:52,928
nor zey hobn dokh geharget oykhet, di ukraynishe hobn geharget mayn bruder.

498
00:27:52,928 --> 00:27:57,545
UNK ge- mitgearbet mit di GERMANIM, ⟨PASHUT MEOD⟩... ha?

499
00:27:57,041 --> 00:27:58,041
HAFSAKA.

